comments: Campazzo (DEN) initiates contact across White's (BOS) side and right arm during his upward shooting motion.
Smart (BOS) and Nnaji (DEN) engage and disengage with one another as they each attempt to obtain rebounding position.
Jokic (DEN) and White (BOS) engage and disengage with one another following the expiration of the pick.
Jokic (DEN) maintains a rested forearm on White's (BOS) front and marginal contact occurs as Jokic establishes position near the elbow.

Tatum (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball as simultaneous marginal forearm contact occurs with Jokic (DEN). White (BOS) maintains a rested hand to Jokic's front and marginal contact occurs prior to Jokic passing.

Williams III (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Nnaji (DEN) prior to any incidental arm contact occurring. Prior to the dislodge, Brown (BOS) jumps toward Nnaji and marginal body contact occurs during Nnaji's upward shooting motion.
Campazzo (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Brown (BOS) during the drive.
Williams III (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Nnaji's (DEN) path and absorbs the contact.
Williams III (BOS) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.

Smart (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Nnaji's (DEN) path and absorbs the contact. Nnaji goes to, not through, Smart's space as the pick is set and marginal contact occurs to Smart's front.

Campazzo (DEN) initiates contact with Smart's (BOS) front that affects Smart's FOM off-ball. After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined no further penalty would be assessed for the contact thereafter.
Tatum (BOS) and Barton (DEN) engage and disengage with one another following the inbound.
Williams III (BOS) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Gordon (DEN) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
White (BOS) is retreating alongside Jokic's (DEN) path and marginal body contact occurs during Jokic's drive.
Jokic (DEN) brings his off-arm toward White's (BOS) front and marginal contact occurs as Jokic drives toward the lane. White's reaction is not commensurate with the level of contact.
Williams III (BOS) brings his left hand toward Jokic's (DEN) side and marginal contact occurs during Jokic's upward shooting motion.
Campazzo (DEN) moves forward toward Tatum (BOS) and marginal body contact occurs as Tatum starts his dribble along the sideline.
Jokic (DEN) commits a take foul on Smart (BOS).
Williams III (BOS) initiates contact with Campazzo's (DEN) side, dislodging Campazzo from position as he moves to retrieve the inbound.
Gordon (DEN) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
Tatum (BOS) engages and disengages with Nnaji (DEN) as Nnaji moves to set the pick.
White (BOS) and Nnaji (DEN) engage and disengage with one another as the pick expires and the oncoming screen approaches.
Jokic (DEN) brings his off-arm toward White's (BOS) front and marginal contact occurs as White is retreating toward the baseline during the drive.
Tatum (BOS) extends for the rebound and some contact occurs with Jokic's (DEN) left arm, causing Jokic to momentarily lose control of the ball, which he quickly recovers.
Tatum (BOS) brings his hand toward Jokic's (DEN) back and marginal contact occurs during Jokic's upward shooting motion.
